<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>물품 등록/수정 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex">
  {{> common/sidebar-item-manager}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="content-wrapper flex-1 p-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
              <i data-feather="package" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{pageTitle}}</h1>
              <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">병원에서 사용하는 물품의 재고와 최소 수량을 관리합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/item-manager/item-list" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700">
            목록으로 돌아가기
          </a>
        </div>

        {{#errorMessage}}
        <div class="p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl text-sm text-red-700">{{errorMessage}}</div>
        {{/errorMessage}}

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8">
          <form method="post" action="/item-manager/item-form/save" class="space-y-6">
            <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
            {{#form.edit}}
            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{form.id}}">
            {{/form.edit}}

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">물품명</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="package" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    name="name"
                    value="{{form.name}}"
                    required
                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none"
                    placeholder="예: 알코올 솜"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">카테고리</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="layers" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <select
                    name="category"
                    required
                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white"
                  >
                    <option value="MEDICAL_SUPPLIES" {{#form.medicalSupplies}}selected{{/form.medicalSupplies}}>의료소모품</option>
                    <option value="MEDICAL_EQUIPMENT" {{#form.medicalEquipment}}selected{{/form.medicalEquipment}}>의료기기</option>
                    <option value="GENERAL_SUPPLIES" {{#form.generalSupplies}}selected{{/form.generalSupplies}}>사무/비품</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">현재 재고 수량</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="hash" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    name="quantity"
                    value="{{form.quantity}}"
                    required
                    min="0"
                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">최소 유지 수량</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="hash" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    name="minQuantity"
                    value="{{form.minQuantity}}"
                    required
                    min="0"
                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-end gap-3">
              <a href="/item-manager/item-list" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                취소
              </a>
              <button type="submit" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                <i data-feather="save" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                저장하기
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>feather.replace();</script>
</body>
</html>
